      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WINSOME RAMBO (6) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when seventh at Wentworth Park over 520m behind King Of Gods (30.44) in a NG. Placed at his previous run. Has good early speed and can overcome the tricky draw. Ready to return to form. SPRING WITNESS (1) was in the money last time at this track (30.07) in a Grade 5, finishing a 4.5 lengths third. Has two wins already from this draw. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. WINSOME STORM (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (30.11) in a NG at Wentworth Park. Solid record here at this trip including three wins. Should be about the mark. BIG TOWN TILLY (3) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
